Package magellan.client.swing.tasks

Class TaskTablePanel.UpdateEventDispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • magellan.client.swing.tasks.TaskTablePanel.UpdateEventDispatcher
  • Enclosing class:
    TaskTablePanel
    protected final class TaskTablePanel.UpdateEventDispatcher
extends java.lang.Object
    This class registers and handles events in a separate thread. Events are first enqueued here and than handled one by one in the refreshThread.
    Version:
    1.0, Aug 23, 2008
    Author:
    stm
